high_descs: Go straight near on the countertop.
Pick the cooking utensil (pot) kept near to the table.
Go straight turn left near to the sink.
Place the pot to the sink.
Collect the utensil from the countertop and clean it in the sink.
Place the pot near to the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Pick the pot clean to the sink and place to the countertop

high_descs: Turn around and go to the first countertop in the kitchen behind you.
Pick up the black pot on the counter.
Go around the counter to the sink.
Put the pot in the sink, turn the water on, and take it out.
Face the corner where the two countertops meet near the sink.
Place the pot on the countertop to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed Pot on the CounterTop next to the sink.

high_descs: Turn around to reach the counter top.
Pick up the pot from the counter top.
Reach around the counter top to reach the sink.
Wash the pot in the sink and take it out.
Turn to reach the counter top on the left.
Put the pot on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed pot on the counter top.
